ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
Subject(Wheat, extra strong wheat, red winter wheat, amber durum wheat, barley and designated barley) Freight Adjustment Factors ** APPROVAL THEREOF **
PrecisOrder approving the amounts established by the Canadian Wheat Board of the FREIGHT ADJUSTMENT FACTORS for certain delivery points for WHEAT, EXTRA STRONG WHEAT, RED WINTER WHEAT, AMBER DURUM WHEAT, BARLEY and DESIGNATED BARLEY to be delivered to The Canadian Wheat Board during the 2009-10 pool period, beginning August 1, 2009.
